<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA48">
<l>tirumārpi lēṉac ceḻumaruppaip pārkkum</l>
<l>perumāṉ piṟaikkoḻuntai nōkku - morunā</l>
<l>ḷitumatiyeṉ ṟoṉṟāka viṉṟaḷavun tērā</l>
<l>tatumatiyoṉ ṟillā varā</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It looks out for the rich tusk of the boar on the sacred chest.</l>
<l>It regards the sprout of the lord’s crescent moon, up to today</l>
<l>it doesn’t understands positively that this is the one-day moon,</l>
<l>that snake without any mind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
